overview: Girlfriends Films is back and proud to present the 61st edition of Lesbian Seductions! Mindi Mink, Romi Rain and a bevy of beautiful girls know that their only sin is the unconditional love of another woman! The revealing, twisted road from desire to pursuit and surrender is one you don't want to miss!
tagline: The revealing twisted road from desire to pursuit and surrender.
title: Lesbian Seductions: Older/Younger 61
